Package: gbif.range
Version: 1.5.3
Title: Tools for GBIF Retrieval and Ecoregion-Based Species Range Mapping
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports: terra, rgbif, CoordinateCleaner, sf, ClusterR, FNN, geometry,
 cluster, rnaturalearth, mclust, methods, utils, zip, class,
 NMOF
Suggests:
    data.table,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Description: Provides a workflow to retrieve, filter, and analyze GBIF
 occurrence records and to generate ecologically informed species
 range maps using downloaded or custom ecoregions. The package
 includes tools for querying the GBIF backbone taxonomy, counting
 or downloading occurrences, creating custom ecoregion layers,
 building range maps, and evaluating them against independent
 validation data.
